        <body>
            <pb n="1"/>
            <p><persName role="author">J. ABRAHAM</persName>,</p>
            <p>Attorney and <sic>Counsellor</sic> at Law,</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">AND</p>
            <p>Solicitor in Chancery.</p>
            <p rend="align(right)"><placeName>Cincinnati</placeName>, <date>9<hi rend="sup">th</hi>
                    June 1854</date></p>
            <p>
                <addressee>Revd I Leeser</addressee>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">Dear Sir/</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">I enclose $5 which you will please<lb/> credit me with. I cannot
                omit the opportunity<lb/> to express my humble approbation of your course with<lb/>
                respect to the wise Dr I trust you receive more satis<lb/>-factory assurances of the
                confidence reposed in you by<lb/> all the community. I coincide precisely with
                your<lb/> views which if I understand them correctly, are, that<lb/> many
                improvements may be made in our forms by a<lb/>
                <hi rend="underline">duly</hi> &amp; <hi rend="underline">properly constituted</hi>
                body, but for any man to<lb/> lop off here, another there, and a thin elsewhere,
                there<lb/> can be no limit &amp; the tree would eventually be left not<lb/> only
                without fruit but void of branches &amp; finally<lb/> the trunk &amp; root would
                disappear; combat such result<lb/> you do your duty only, go on with the good
                work<lb/> you will finally reap the reward. I wish<lb/> you to insert in your cover
                the card I annex &amp; let<lb/> me know what it will cost pr annum</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">I am</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">your friend</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">
                <persName role="author">Joseph Abraham</persName>
            </p>
            <p>(Over)</p>
            <pb n="4"/>
            <p>
                <addressee>Revd I Leeser</addressee>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">Edr Occident</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">
                <del>
                    <placeName>New York</placeName>
                </del>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">
                <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(3)">
                <placeName>Pa</placeName>
            </p>
        </body>
